ard – 1 cuộn – có giá 10,230 vnđ.</span></span></span></li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	</span><li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"background-color: white; font-size: 14px;\">Băng keo 2 mặt vàng dầu 12mm 10Yard – 1 cuộn – có giá 2,970 vnđ.</span></span></span></li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	</span><li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"background-color: white; font-size: 14px;\">Băng keo 2 mặt vàng dầu 24mm 10Yard – 1 cuộn – có giá 5,335 vnđ.</span></span></span></li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	</span><li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"background-color: white; font-size: 14px;\">Băng keo 2 mặt vàng dầu 12mm 18Yard – 1 cuộn – có giá 4,400 vnđ.</span></span></span></li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\r\n</span></ul><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\r\n\r\n</span><p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"color: black; font-size: 14px;\">Trên đây chi là mức giá tham khảo cho một sản phẩm của đơn vị chúng tôi. Đây là dòng keo duy nhất có cấu trúc tạo thành rất nhiều lớp.</span></span></p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\r\n\r\n</span><p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\r\n\r\n</span><h2 style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Cambria,serif\"><span style=\"color:#4f81bd\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Cơ sở đang kinh doanh băng keo 2 mặt </span></strong></span></span></span></h2><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\r\n\r\n</span><p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\